489
00:32:50,900 --> 00:32:53,100
<font color="yellow">What? Gun Woo?</font>

490
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:54,840
<font color="yellow">Is Gun Woo in this, too?</font>

491
00:32:56,540 --> 00:32:59,140
