00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:42,570
<font color="yellow">You wanted to get the highest price by putting us against each other.</font>

503
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:45,040
<font color="yellow">You should hold back a fight and bargain on businesses.</font>

504
00:33:45,670 --> 00:33:48,040
<font color="yellow">That's what business is, isn't it?</font>

505
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:51,540
<font color="yellow">I'll give you 400,000 shares and no more.</font>

