00:34:30,370 --> 00:34:31,470
<font color="yellow">Are you serious?</font>

518
00:34:32,140 --> 00:34:34,170
<font color="yellow">Mum will be so mad.</font>

519
00:34:35,140 --> 00:34:37,910
<font color="yellow">This is about the management rights.</font>

520
00:34:37,910 --> 00:34:39,440
<font color="yellow">I can't give it up.</font>

521
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:44,720
<font color="yellow">Tell Gun Woo that we're sealing the deal with this one.</font>

522
00:34:44,720 --> 00:34:45,770
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

523
00:34:47,940 --> 00:34:49,470
<font color="yellow">He gave up 500,000 shares.</font>

