00:36:39,100 --> 00:36:40,200
<font color="yellow">Be careful, Chairman.</font>

544
00:36:40,970 --> 00:36:42,100
<font color="yellow">For what?</font>

545
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:45,010
<font color="yellow">Those people are eyeing us in strange ways.</font>

