00:37:45,540 --> 00:37:46,540
<font color="yellow">It was nothing.</font>

555
00:37:46,540 --> 00:37:47,600
<font color="yellow">Don't say that.</font>

556
00:37:49,270 --> 00:37:51,570
<font color="yellow">Let me see. Is it bad?</font>

