00:38:57,070 --> 00:38:59,540
<font color="yellow">We'll take Dodo Hotel instead.</font>

581
00:38:59,540 --> 00:39:02,200
<font color="yellow">We're giving up on Gun Woo, so this works for us.</font>

582
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:04,800
<font color="yellow">Do you really think that Gwang Woo and Chairwoman Hwang...</font>

583
00:39:05,270 --> 00:39:06,670
