584
00:39:07,440 --> 00:39:08,990
<font color="yellow">at the general meeting?</font>

585
00:39:08,990 --> 00:39:10,410
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

586
00:39:10,410 --> 00:39:12,270
