00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:03,320
<font color="yellow">It can't be done by then.</font>

621
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:04,540
<font color="yellow">That's too bad.</font>

622
00:41:05,370 --> 00:41:06,900
<font color="yellow">After the general meeting,</font>

