00:41:13,970 --> 00:41:15,240
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

627
00:41:15,240 --> 00:41:17,770
<font color="yellow">Can you organise a family meeting as soon as possible?</font>

628
00:41:18,670 --> 00:41:20,470
