00:41:38,170 --> 00:41:40,440
<font color="yellow">You're the one who verbally abused me.</font>

634
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:42,540
<font color="yellow">We wouldn't be in this mess if you were nice.</font>

635
00:41:42,540 --> 00:41:43,570
<font color="yellow">Tonight,</font>

636
00:41:44,900 --> 00:41:46,650
<font color="yellow">call the kids over.</font>

637
00:41:46,650 --> 00:41:47,970
<font color="yellow">What for?</font>

638
00:41:48,370 --> 00:41:49,710
<font color="yellow">To write a will?</font>

639
00:41:49,710 --> 00:41:50,970
<font color="yellow">Before the general meeting,</font>

640
00:41:51,470 --> 00:41:54,270
<font color="yellow">we need to get our stories straight as a family.</font>

641
00:41:54,740 --> 00:41:56,100
<font color="yellow">Or else,</font>

642
00:41:56,570 --> 00:41:58,800
<font color="yellow">everyone will find out what a mess we are.</font>

