00:42:00,370 --> 00:42:02,440
<font color="yellow">Are you trying to save face?</font>

644
00:42:03,340 --> 00:42:04,800
<font color="yellow">To rich people like us,</font>

645
00:42:05,970 --> 00:42:10,100
<font color="yellow">our reputation is our brand, you foolish woman.</font>

646
00:42:10,100 --> 00:42:13,470
<font color="yellow">Who are you calling foolish, you senile, old rat?</font>

647
00:42:17,570 --> 00:42:18,600
<font color="yellow">Mr Gong.</font>

648
00:42:19,570 --> 00:42:21,450
<font color="yellow">Start looking for a house.</font>

649
00:42:21,450 --> 00:42:23,320
<font color="yellow">What for, Ma'am?</font>

650
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:24,700
<font color="yellow">Once the general meeting's over,</font>

651
00:42:25,200 --> 00:42:27,170
<font color="yellow">I will kick you both out of my house.</font>

652
00:42:27,970 --> 00:42:30,970
<font color="yellow">Find a place before then or you'll end up on the streets.</font>

653
00:42:35,170 --> 00:42:36,800
<font color="yellow">She's going too far.</font>

654
00:42:37,340 --> 00:42:38,740
<font color="yellow">First, she slapped you.</font>

655
00:42:39,370 --> 00:42:40,570
<font color="yellow">And now, she's kicking...</font>

656
00:42:40,570 --> 00:42:42,720
<font color="yellow">I told you not to mention that.</font>

657
00:42:42,720 --> 00:42:44,010
<font color="yellow">Sorry, Sir.</font>

658
00:42:45,640 --> 00:42:46,840
<font color="yellow">Find a place.</font>

659
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:49,540
<font color="yellow">A small and run-down place.</font>

660
00:42:49,540 --> 00:42:50,600
<font color="yellow">Pardon?</font>

661
00:42:50,970 --> 00:42:52,470
<font color="yellow">That hag and Gwang Woo...</font>

662
00:42:54,200 --> 00:42:55,640
<font color="yellow">will need to move out...</font>

663
00:42:56,470 --> 00:42:58,370
<font color="yellow">after the general meeting.</font>

664
00:42:59,370 --> 00:43:00,570
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

665
00:43:06,740 --> 00:43:08,360
<font color="yellow">I can't believe...</font>

666
00:43:08,360 --> 00:43:11,100
<font color="yellow">you're attending our family gathering.</font>

667
00:43:12,640 --> 00:43:14,090
<font color="yellow">Our father invited her...</font>

668
00:43:14,090 --> 00:43:16,200
<font color="yellow">as Dodo Group's legal counsel.</font>

669
00:43:17,640 --> 00:43:20,090
<font color="yellow">Will her presence change anything?</font>

670
00:43:20,090 --> 00:43:22,470
<font color="yellow">It won't, so don't mind her.</font>

671
00:43:26,770 --> 00:43:27,870
<font color="yellow">Welcome, Chairman Kang.</font>

672
00:43:28,470 --> 00:43:29,470
<font color="yellow">Hi, Mum.</font>

673
00:43:31,100 --> 00:43:32,570
<font color="yellow">How have you been?</font>

674
00:43:32,570 --> 00:43:35,820
<font color="yellow">Money really does change a man. You look so much more handsome.</font>

675
00:43:35,820 --> 00:43:36,840
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

676
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:39,340
<font color="yellow">Where is Dad?</font>

677
00:43:39,340 --> 00:43:40,470
<font color="yellow">He'll be here soon.</font>

678
00:43:40,840 --> 00:43:42,170
<font color="yellow">Have a seat.</font>

679
00:43:53,840 --> 00:43:54,970
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

680
00:43:56,640 --> 00:43:58,340
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

681
00:43:58,770 --> 00:44:00,000
<font color="yellow">I was hungry.</font>

682
00:44:00,570 --> 00:44:05,040
<font color="yellow">The others are downstairs waiting for you to join them.</font>

683
00:44:05,040 --> 00:44:06,070
<font color="yellow">What for?</font>

684
00:44:06,840 --> 00:44:08,340
<font color="yellow">Is it someone's birthday?</font>

685
00:44:08,670 --> 00:44:11,950
<font color="yellow">Didn't you tell everyone to come over?</font>

686
00:44:11,950 --> 00:44:12,970
<font color="yellow">Did I?</font>

687
00:44:13,670 --> 00:44:14,670
<font color="yellow">Right.</font>

688
00:44:15,170 --> 00:44:16,170
<font color="yellow">I did.</font>

689
00:44:17,370 --> 00:44:19,840
<font color="yellow">It's a very important day.</font>

690
00:44:22,840 --> 00:44:25,070
<font color="yellow">Sir. Sir.</font>

691
00:44:25,770 --> 00:44:27,370
<font color="yellow">Sit in the wheelchair.</font>

692
00:44:27,370 --> 00:44:30,600
<font color="yellow">That's right. I forgot.</font>

693
00:44:34,740 --> 00:44:36,070
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

694
00:44:38,470 --> 00:44:39,640
<font color="yellow">Come on, push me.</font>

695
00:44:40,070 --> 00:44:43,170
<font color="yellow">If you're too tired, you can postpone...</font>

696
00:44:43,170 --> 00:44:45,100
<font color="yellow">I'm fine. Take me downstairs.</font>

697
00:44:51,840 --> 00:44:53,840
<font color="yellow">I called you all...</font>

698
00:44:54,570 --> 00:44:55,640
<font color="yellow">so we could...</font>

699
00:44:56,840 --> 00:44:58,470
<font color="yellow">go through the details...</font>

700
00:44:59,540 --> 00:45:01,960
<font color="yellow">before the general meeting.</font>

701
00:45:01,960 --> 00:45:04,370
<font color="yellow">Everything's sorted. What's left to discuss?</font>

702
00:45:06,200 --> 00:45:08,070
<font color="yellow">- Jae Man.
-  Yes.</font>

703
00:45:10,740 --> 00:45:13,270
<font color="yellow">My son-in-law signed this.</font>

704
00:45:13,900 --> 00:45:17,570
<font color="yellow">This power of attorney states that he'll transfer his shares...</font>

705
00:45:18,170 --> 00:45:19,670
<font color="yellow">to Chairwoman Hwang.</font>

706
00:45:28,270 --> 00:45:29,470
<font color="yellow">Don't worry, Father.</font>

707
00:45:29,900 --> 00:45:31,840
<font color="yellow">Shin Young's shares of Dodo Pharmaceutical...</font>

708
00:45:31,840 --> 00:45:33,970
<font color="yellow">That deal's been made already.</font>

709
00:45:34,570 --> 00:45:36,740
<font color="yellow">I'll be getting those tomorrow.</font>

710
00:45:37,570 --> 00:45:39,570
<font color="yellow">This isn't what we agreed on.</font>

711
00:45:39,570 --> 00:45:43,610
<font color="yellow">I thought the deal with you would stand, but...</font>

712
00:45:43,610 --> 00:45:46,170
<font color="yellow">Gwang Woo's terms were better.</font>

713
00:45:47,170 --> 00:45:49,070
<font color="yellow">Business is about profit.</font>

714
00:45:49,540 --> 00:45:50,570
<font color="yellow">It can't be helped.</font>

715
00:45:53,770 --> 00:45:55,570
<font color="yellow">Sorry, Dad.</font>

716
00:45:56,070 --> 00:45:57,570
<font color="yellow">Mum said that...</font>

717
00:45:57,570 --> 00:46:00,610
<font color="yellow">she'd give me Dodo Hotel.</font>

718
00:46:00,610 --> 00:46:01,700
<font color="yellow">What does she mean?</font>

719
00:46:02,100 --> 00:46:03,730
<font color="yellow">You said it would be mine.</font>

720
00:46:03,730 --> 00:46:05,350
<font color="yellow">It turned out a little differently.</font>

721
00:46:05,350 --> 00:46:08,070
<font color="yellow">I'll give you the golf course in Yongin instead.</font>

722
00:46:08,070 --> 00:46:09,670
<font color="yellow">A golf course isn't a hotel.</font>

723
00:46:10,470 --> 00:46:12,730
<font color="yellow">You can't have Il Jae's power of attorney.</font>

724
00:46:12,730 --> 00:46:14,370
<font color="yellow">- Ji Soo.
-  Add to that...</font>

725
00:46:14,840 --> 00:46:17,370
<font color="yellow">the home shopping channel.</font>

726
00:46:17,770 --> 00:46:19,900
<font color="yellow">Jae Man, the home shopping channel...</font>

727
00:46:19,900 --> 00:46:20,970
<font color="yellow">I want that instead.</font>

728
00:46:22,270 --> 00:46:25,050
<font color="yellow">That might be enough to placate me.</font>

729
00:46:25,050 --> 00:46:28,470
<font color="yellow">Mum, isn't that a bit too much?</font>

730
00:46:28,470 --> 00:46:29,470
<font color="yellow">Be quiet.</font>

731
00:46:31,540 --> 00:46:34,540
<font color="yellow">Fine. The golf course and the home shopping channel.</font>

732
00:46:35,900 --> 00:46:38,570
<font color="yellow">Someone wants to make his illegitimate son his heir.</font>

733
00:46:39,470 --> 00:46:41,840
<font color="yellow">What wouldn't I do for my own flesh and blood?</font>

734
00:46:42,170 --> 00:46:43,200
<font color="yellow">Hey!</font>

735
00:46:48,540 --> 00:46:49,570
<font color="yellow">All of you.</font>

736
00:46:50,340 --> 00:46:52,770
<font color="yellow">What are you doing with my assets?</font>

737
00:46:53,640 --> 00:46:55,340
<font color="yellow">Every company in Dodo Group...</font>

738
00:46:56,370 --> 00:46:59,170
<font color="yellow">I built up from scratch!</font>

739
00:47:00,070 --> 00:47:01,170
<font color="yellow">How dare you?</font>

740
00:47:02,840 --> 00:47:06,070
<font color="yellow">What makes you think you can split them among yourselves?</font>

741
00:47:06,070 --> 00:47:07,770
<font color="yellow">Do you still think they're yours?</font>

742
00:47:08,270 --> 00:47:09,520
<font color="yellow">You're wrong!</font>

743
00:47:09,520 --> 00:47:11,070
<font color="yellow">Everything will become mine...</font>

744
00:47:11,470 --> 00:47:13,100
<font color="yellow">at the general meeting!</font>

745
00:47:13,100 --> 00:47:14,840
<font color="yellow">The meeting hasn't happened yet.</font>

746
00:47:15,640 --> 00:47:18,610
<font color="yellow">Don't celebrate before the fight even begins.</font>

747
00:47:18,610 --> 00:47:20,160
<font color="yellow">That's just foolish.</font>

748
00:47:20,160 --> 00:47:22,370
<font color="yellow">We're celebrating because we can.</font>

749
00:47:22,370 --> 00:47:24,100
<font color="yellow">We're used to partying.</font>

750
00:47:25,070 --> 00:47:26,260
<font color="yellow">Did you see this?</font>

751
00:47:26,260 --> 00:47:29,120
<font color="yellow">Other than you and I, the rest are like hyenas.</font>

752
00:47:29,120 --> 00:47:30,770
<font color="yellow">What? Hyenas?</font>

753
00:47:30,770 --> 00:47:33,240
<font color="yellow">I'll toss them some rotten meat and sort them out.</font>

754
00:47:33,240 --> 00:47:34,400
<font color="yellow">Don't you worry.</font>

755
00:47:36,070 --> 00:47:37,470
<font color="yellow">I think I should leave.</font>

756
00:47:38,100 --> 00:47:40,400
<font color="yellow">Already? You haven't eaten yet.</font>

757
00:47:40,870 --> 00:47:42,170
<font color="yellow">You can take your time.</font>

758
00:47:42,170 --> 00:47:43,540
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan.</font>

759
00:47:43,540 --> 00:47:46,300
<font color="yellow">I guess you don't keep your private life and work separate.</font>

760
00:47:46,300 --> 00:47:49,140
<font color="yellow">It's a business transaction. Watch what you say.</font>

761
00:47:49,140 --> 00:47:52,640
<font color="yellow">When it comes to business, I'm the better catch.</font>

762
00:47:52,640 --> 00:47:55,170
<font color="yellow">Gwang Woo, don't get ahead of yourself.</font>

763
00:47:55,840 --> 00:47:59,100
<font color="yellow">I did it to benefit Shin Young, not to help you.</font>

764
00:48:00,340 --> 00:48:01,400
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

765
00:48:05,240 --> 00:48:06,970
<font color="yellow">If this is it,</font>

766
00:48:07,770 --> 00:48:09,170
<font color="yellow">we should leave, too.</font>

767
00:48:09,840 --> 00:48:11,140
<font color="yellow">Okay, Dad.</font>

768
00:48:11,140 --> 00:48:12,170
<font color="yellow">Jae Man.</font>

769
00:48:14,270 --> 00:48:16,570
<font color="yellow">What did you bring as my birthday present?</font>

770
00:48:18,140 --> 00:48:19,170
<font color="yellow">Don't tell me...</font>

771
00:48:19,970 --> 00:48:21,470
<font color="yellow">you came empty-handed.</font>

772
00:48:23,670 --> 00:48:26,170
<font color="yellow">Bok Shin, go and get...</font>

773
00:48:27,040 --> 00:48:28,240
<font color="yellow">the birthday cake.</font>

774
00:48:28,940 --> 00:48:29,970
<font color="yellow">Right now.</font>

775
00:48:31,570 --> 00:48:32,600
<font color="yellow">What cake?</font>

776
00:48:33,600 --> 00:48:35,240
<font color="yellow">Today's my birthday.</font>

777
00:48:35,940 --> 00:48:38,370
<font color="yellow">I'll cut the cake...</font>

778
00:48:40,170 --> 00:48:41,270
<font color="yellow">and blow out the candles.</font>

779
00:48:42,170 --> 00:48:43,840
<font color="yellow">You were born in the winter.</font>

780
00:48:43,840 --> 00:48:45,370
<font color="yellow">What are you talking about?</font>

781
00:48:45,870 --> 00:48:49,170
<font color="yellow">You cooked me birthday soup.</font>

782
00:48:49,600 --> 00:48:51,470
<font color="yellow">Thank you so much.</font>

783
00:48:53,400 --> 00:48:54,470
<font color="yellow">Father.</font>

784
00:48:55,070 --> 00:48:56,100
<font color="yellow">Gwang Woo.</font>

785
00:48:56,770 --> 00:48:58,870
<font color="yellow">Go and get your grandmother.</font>

786
00:48:59,870 --> 00:49:01,220
<font color="yellow">Let's eat.</font>

787
00:49:01,220 --> 00:49:03,300
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with you?</font>

788
00:49:04,170 --> 00:49:05,370
<font color="yellow">Get the cake.</font>

789
00:49:11,070 --> 00:49:12,590
<font color="yellow">When did this start?</font>

790
00:49:12,590 --> 00:49:16,540
<font color="yellow">He'd been a bit forgetful, but it was never this serious.</font>

791
00:49:16,540 --> 00:49:20,570
<font color="yellow">Wasn't he tested when he was last admitted?</font>

792
00:49:20,570 --> 00:49:22,340
<font color="yellow">The doctor said he was fine.</font>

793
00:49:22,340 --> 00:49:24,310
<font color="yellow">What happened to him then?</font>

794
00:49:24,310 --> 00:49:25,770
<font color="yellow">It must be the drug's side effect.</font>

795
00:49:27,270 --> 00:49:28,450
<font color="yellow">Side effect?</font>

796
00:49:28,450 --> 00:49:32,740
<font color="yellow">The doctor said this could happen if the drug doesn't suit him.</font>

797
00:49:33,870 --> 00:49:35,770
<font color="yellow">Is he on his way?</font>

798
00:49:36,170 --> 00:49:37,370
<font color="yellow">He'll be here soon.</font>

799
00:49:41,370 --> 00:49:42,740
<font color="yellow">It won't be dementia.</font>

800
00:49:43,870 --> 00:49:44,870
<font color="yellow">No?</font>

801
00:49:45,970 --> 00:49:49,870
<font color="yellow">To me, it looked just like dementia.</font>

802
00:49:50,600 --> 00:49:53,470
<font color="yellow">The test he got a few days ago came back clean.</font>

803
00:49:54,040 --> 00:49:56,970
<font color="yellow">You can't be sure. Have him tested again.</font>

804
00:50:00,470 --> 00:50:02,670
<font color="yellow">If we can have him ruled mentally incapable,</font>

805
00:50:03,370 --> 00:50:05,070
<font color="yellow">we could take...</font>

806
00:50:05,870 --> 00:50:08,970
<font color="yellow">everything under his name.</font>

807
00:50:18,170 --> 00:50:21,340
<font color="yellow">That family is much more twisted than I thought.</font>

808
00:50:23,070 --> 00:50:26,310
<font color="yellow">It's gotten worse than when I was Chief Secretary.</font>

809
00:50:26,310 --> 00:50:27,470
<font color="yellow">I'm glad we were there.</font>

810
00:50:28,600 --> 00:50:32,230
<font color="yellow">I got to see the family for what they're really like.</font>

811
00:50:32,230 --> 00:50:36,770
<font color="yellow">They all have different ideas. That leaves us with many openings.</font>

812
00:50:38,040 --> 00:50:39,070
<font color="yellow">I think...</font>

813
00:50:39,770 --> 00:50:41,870
<font color="yellow">we can push ahead as planned.</font>

814
00:50:51,470 --> 00:50:52,970
<font color="yellow">Don't worry, Gun Woo.</font>

815
00:50:53,740 --> 00:50:56,400
<font color="yellow">He won't give in just like that.</font>

816
00:50:57,500 --> 00:50:58,970
<font color="yellow">The general meeting's the problem.</font>

817
00:51:00,500 --> 00:51:04,600
<font color="yellow">Now, Gwang Woo owns Shin Young's Dodo Pharmaceutical shares.</font>

818
00:51:05,140 --> 00:51:08,400
<font color="yellow">My chance of beating them is now much slimmer.</font>

819
00:51:09,100 --> 00:51:10,140
<font color="yellow">If I lose,</font>

820
00:51:10,670 --> 00:51:12,840
<font color="yellow">Father will suffer even more.</font>

821
00:51:15,100 --> 00:51:16,170
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

822
00:51:17,240 --> 00:51:19,970
<font color="yellow">I wanted to be of help to you.</font>

823
00:51:22,340 --> 00:51:24,170
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan hates me...</font>

824
00:51:24,740 --> 00:51:26,070
<font color="yellow">and I understand.</font>

825
00:51:26,870 --> 00:51:28,740
<font color="yellow">I was duped into it by Il Jae,</font>

826
00:51:29,740 --> 00:51:33,870
<font color="yellow">but I played a part in framing him for murder.</font>

827
00:51:40,170 --> 00:51:43,070
<font color="yellow">Stop. You've had enough to drink.</font>

828
00:51:45,670 --> 00:51:47,770
<font color="yellow">I'd like to be alone tonight.</font>

829
00:51:49,170 --> 00:51:50,300
<font color="yellow">Mr Kim.</font>

830
00:51:52,840 --> 00:51:54,040
<font color="yellow">Take her home.</font>

831
00:51:54,470 --> 00:51:55,740
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir.</font>

832
00:51:55,740 --> 00:51:58,400
<font color="yellow">You don't have to. Look after him instead.</font>

833
00:52:00,970 --> 00:52:02,340
<font color="yellow">Don't drink too much.</font>

834
00:52:23,340 --> 00:52:26,400
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you tell her you have a plan B?</font>

835
00:52:27,140 --> 00:52:28,170
<font color="yellow">Do you know...</font>

836
00:52:29,470 --> 00:52:31,770
<font color="yellow">what the hardest thing in the world is for me?</font>

837
00:52:33,570 --> 00:52:35,740
<font color="yellow">It's to make a woman love me.</font>

838
00:52:37,740 --> 00:52:39,070
<font color="yellow">I need a strategy.</font>

839
00:52:40,770 --> 00:52:43,670
<font color="yellow">A plan to make Soo Yeon...</font>

840
00:52:45,770 --> 00:52:47,300
<font color="yellow">side with me completely.</font>

841
00:53:02,870 --> 00:53:04,070
<font color="yellow">It's me, Soo Yeon.</font>

842
00:53:05,240 --> 00:53:07,570
<font color="yellow">I'd like to meet you.</font>

843
00:53:09,240 --> 00:53:10,270
<font color="yellow">It's a bit late.</font>

844
00:53:10,970 --> 00:53:11,970
<font color="yellow">Have a seat.</font>

845
00:53:18,300 --> 00:53:21,770
<font color="yellow">I came to ask you for a favour.</font>

846
00:53:22,470 --> 00:53:26,370
<font color="yellow">Go on. Any request from you is worth hearing.</font>

847
00:53:28,500 --> 00:53:31,670
<font color="yellow">It's about Shin Young's shares of Dodo Pharmaceutical.</font>

848
00:53:32,600 --> 00:53:34,600
<font color="yellow">Can you give them to Gun Woo?</font>

849
00:53:37,170 --> 00:53:38,940
<font color="yellow">He feels terrible...</font>

850
00:53:39,340 --> 00:53:41,770
<font color="yellow">for what he did to you.</font>

851
00:53:42,600 --> 00:53:45,740
<font color="yellow">He even betrayed Il Jae, knowing what a loss it would be.</font>

852
00:53:52,070 --> 00:53:54,310
<font color="yellow">It wouldn't have been a loss had I helped him.</font>

853
00:53:54,310 --> 00:53:56,570
<font color="yellow">- Sir.
-  I'm a businessman.</font>

854
00:53:57,470 --> 00:53:59,140
<font color="yellow">I do the math.</font>

855
00:54:01,140 --> 00:54:02,870
<font color="yellow">I showed you favour...</font>

856
00:54:03,870 --> 00:54:06,100
<font color="yellow">because I thought we were on the same page.</font>

857
00:54:06,840 --> 00:54:08,840
<font color="yellow">The loss of a sibling hurts.</font>

858
00:54:09,470 --> 00:54:11,370
<font color="yellow">Gun Woo wouldn't know, but I do.</font>

859
00:54:14,170 --> 00:54:16,870
<font color="yellow">You're soft-hearted so I understand why you're doing this.</font>

860
00:54:17,670 --> 00:54:19,940
<font color="yellow">But Gun Woo isn't the good man...</font>

861
00:54:20,340 --> 00:54:21,770
<font color="yellow">you think he is.</font>

862
00:54:23,670 --> 00:54:25,340
<font color="yellow">If you ask for such a favour again,</font>

863
00:54:26,040 --> 00:54:27,570
<font color="yellow">I will cut all ties with you.</font>

864
00:55:03,400 --> 00:55:05,670
<font color="yellow">I think a lot of them still want you dead.</font>

865
00:55:23,570 --> 00:55:24,670
<font color="yellow">Guk Cheol.</font>

866
00:55:26,140 --> 00:55:27,400
<font color="yellow">You tried to kill me...</font>

867
00:55:28,870 --> 00:55:30,040
<font color="yellow">when I was in prison, too.</font>

868
00:55:48,570 --> 00:55:50,150
<font color="yellow">Was it another nightmare?</font>

869
00:55:50,150 --> 00:55:53,970
<font color="yellow">Gi Tan now tortures me in my dreams, too.</font>

870
00:55:57,370 --> 00:55:59,820
<font color="yellow">4984, the superintendent wants to see you.</font>

871
00:55:59,820 --> 00:56:01,060
<font color="yellow">What for?</font>

872
00:56:01,060 --> 00:56:02,570
<font color="yellow">Did you ask to be transferred?</font>

873
00:56:02,940 --> 00:56:04,370
<font color="yellow">I did not.</font>

874
00:56:04,970 --> 00:56:06,600
<font color="yellow">Maybe your wife did.</font>

875
00:56:20,370 --> 00:56:22,170
<font color="yellow">- What's going on?
-  I'm sorry.</font>

876
00:56:23,240 --> 00:56:25,470
<font color="yellow">Mr Do wouldn't stop begging.</font>

877
00:56:26,140 --> 00:56:27,470
<font color="yellow">Bring them some coffee.</font>

878
00:56:40,170 --> 00:56:41,840
<font color="yellow">The general meeting's in two days.</font>

879
00:56:42,340 --> 00:56:44,240
<font color="yellow">You gave your shares to Gwang Woo.</font>

880
00:56:45,300 --> 00:56:49,840
<font color="yellow">Did you actually think I would help you?</font>

881
00:56:50,570 --> 00:56:52,740
<font color="yellow">Can I release the evidence of your embezzlement?</font>

882
00:56:53,500 --> 00:56:54,840
<font color="yellow">Sure.</font>

883
00:56:54,840 --> 00:56:57,670
<font color="yellow">I have a lot on you to give to the media.</font>

884
00:57:00,370 --> 00:57:01,740
<font color="yellow">So we both go down?</font>

885
00:57:01,740 --> 00:57:04,370
<font color="yellow">The more you have to lose, the weaker you become.</font>

886
00:57:04,840 --> 00:57:06,340
<font color="yellow">I'm in here, you're out there.</font>

887
00:57:06,940 --> 00:57:08,570
<font color="yellow">Who has the upper hand?</font>

888
00:57:09,570 --> 00:57:11,070
<font color="yellow">Let me tell you one thing.</font>

889
00:57:11,770 --> 00:57:14,400
<font color="yellow">Even without any of your shares, in this general meeting,</font>

890
00:57:15,300 --> 00:57:16,340
<font color="yellow">I will win.</font>

891
00:57:24,470 --> 00:57:27,360
<font color="yellow">What I really want is B World.</font>

892
00:57:27,360 --> 00:57:28,440
<font color="yellow">Your company.</font>

893
00:57:33,670 --> 00:57:34,970
<font color="yellow">Don't even dream of it.</font>

894
00:57:36,170 --> 00:57:38,070
<font color="yellow">Even if a knife's at my neck,</font>

895
00:57:38,400 --> 00:57:40,440
<font color="yellow">I won't give it to you.</font>

896
00:57:40,770 --> 00:57:43,340
<font color="yellow">The knife is already in your neck.</font>

897
00:57:44,140 --> 00:57:45,140
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

898
00:57:46,140 --> 00:57:47,370
<font color="yellow">The coffee...</font>

899
00:57:47,370 --> 00:57:48,540
<font color="yellow">you just...</font>

900
00:57:49,170 --> 00:57:50,240
<font color="yellow">took a sip of.</font>

901
00:57:54,740 --> 00:57:55,740
<font color="yellow">Soon,</font>

902
00:57:56,370 --> 00:57:57,570
<font color="yellow">you will...</font>

903
00:57:58,170 --> 00:57:59,300
<font color="yellow">fall asleep.</font>

904
00:58:03,640 --> 00:58:06,500
<font color="yellow">And I will have your thumbprint on every page of this contract.</font>

905
00:58:09,670 --> 00:58:10,670
<font color="yellow">You can't...</font>

906
00:58:12,240 --> 00:58:14,440
<font color="yellow">take my company with a forged document.</font>

907
00:58:16,240 --> 00:58:17,270
<font color="yellow">I will...</font>

908
00:58:17,840 --> 00:58:20,570
<font color="yellow">not let that happen.</font>

909
00:58:22,870 --> 00:58:24,810
<font color="yellow">Listen carefully before you pass out.</font>

910
00:58:24,810 --> 00:58:27,440
<font color="yellow">You can't do anything. Why not?</font>

911
00:58:27,940 --> 00:58:29,900
<font color="yellow">You'll be in solitary confinement tonight.</font>

912
00:58:32,370 --> 00:58:35,650
<font color="yellow">While you're in there, your company will become mine.</font>

913
00:58:35,650 --> 00:58:37,570
<font color="yellow">And the game will be over.</font>

914
00:58:38,070 --> 00:58:39,770
<font color="yellow">You...</font>

915
00:58:40,170 --> 00:58:42,070
<font color="yellow">You can't...</font>

916
00:58:48,870 --> 00:58:49,870
<font color="yellow">Hold him down.</font>

917
00:59:18,840 --> 00:59:21,940
<font color="yellow">You can't do this to me.</font>

918
00:59:22,740 --> 00:59:26,140
<font color="yellow">I... I made you what you are now.</font>

919
00:59:27,370 --> 00:59:28,440
<font color="yellow">That's why...</font>

920
00:59:29,640 --> 00:59:31,700
<font color="yellow">you shouldn't have touched Soo Yeon.</font>

921
00:59:32,040 --> 00:59:33,370
<font color="yellow">Didn't I warn you?</font>

922
00:59:33,770 --> 00:59:36,560
<font color="yellow">I said you'd make your worst enemy.</font>

923
00:59:36,560 --> 00:59:38,800
<font color="yellow">Do Gun Woo...</font>

924
00:59:39,270 --> 00:59:41,900
<font color="yellow">You took from others all your life.</font>

925
00:59:42,470 --> 00:59:43,940
<font color="yellow">How does it feel to lose something?</font>

926
00:59:45,870 --> 00:59:48,600
<font color="yellow">Gun... Gun Woo...</font>

927
01:00:03,240 --> 01:00:04,570
<font color="yellow">Did you pay them both?</font>

928
01:00:05,100 --> 01:00:06,160
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

929
01:00:06,160 --> 01:00:07,300
<font color="yellow">You can split it.</font>

930
01:00:07,870 --> 01:00:10,240
<font color="yellow">Put him in solitary confinement from now on.</font>

931
01:00:53,940 --> 01:00:54,940
<font color="yellow">Hello, Father.</font>

932
01:00:57,740 --> 01:00:58,770
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

933
01:01:00,740 --> 01:01:01,740
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

934
01:01:03,400 --> 01:01:04,440
<font color="yellow">What did he say?</font>

935
01:01:05,170 --> 01:01:06,270
<font color="yellow">The MK2 vaccine.</font>

936
01:01:06,940 --> 01:01:09,500
<font color="yellow">They got it patented in Korea and America.</font>

937
01:01:10,770 --> 01:01:14,480
<font color="yellow">Then B World's influenza vaccine will take a huge hit.</font>

938
01:01:14,480 --> 01:01:16,170
<font color="yellow">If we sell ours at half price,</font>

939
01:01:16,940 --> 01:01:18,740
<font color="yellow">we could ruin them for good.</font>

940
01:01:21,300 --> 01:01:23,260
<font color="yellow">Is Il Jae in solitary confinement?</font>

941
01:01:23,260 --> 01:01:25,340
<font color="yellow">Yes. According to our contact there,</font>

942
01:01:25,870 --> 01:01:27,070
<font color="yellow">it was Gun Woo's doing.</font>

943
01:01:28,140 --> 01:01:31,210
<font color="yellow">- Can I meet him?
-  It's against the rules,</font>

944
01:01:31,210 --> 01:01:33,770
<font color="yellow">but the superintendent won't be able to say no.</font>

945
01:01:34,100 --> 01:01:36,040
<font color="yellow">Apply for a visit right away.</font>

946
01:01:40,770 --> 01:01:44,140
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't have touched Soo Yeon.</font>

947
01:01:44,140 --> 01:01:46,840
<font color="yellow">You took from others all your life.</font>

948
01:01:46,840 --> 01:01:48,270
<font color="yellow">How does it feel to lose something?</font>

949
01:01:52,740 --> 01:01:54,740
<font color="yellow">4984. You have a visitor.</font>

950
01:02:14,970 --> 01:02:15,970
<font color="yellow">How are you?</font>

951
01:02:18,500 --> 01:02:20,470
<font color="yellow">This brings back memories...</font>

952
01:02:21,170 --> 01:02:22,970
<font color="yellow">of the day you visited me.</font>

953
01:02:25,300 --> 01:02:27,470
<font color="yellow">I enjoyed the pizza you brought so much.</font>

954
01:02:28,170 --> 01:02:29,500
<font color="yellow">I'll return the favour.</font>

955
01:02:31,740 --> 01:02:32,870
<font color="yellow">Have some.</font>

956
01:03:00,640 --> 01:03:02,560
<font color="yellow">(Monster)</font>

957
01:03:02,560 --> 01:03:04,570
<font color="yellow">I gave you a clear warning.</font>

958
01:03:04,570 --> 01:03:06,370
<font color="yellow">Do you think I did it?</font>

959
01:03:06,370 --> 01:03:08,140
<font color="yellow">Marry me, Soo Yeon.</font>

960
01:03:08,870 --> 01:03:10,940
<font color="yellow">Stop Gun Woo from going to the banks.</font>

961
01:03:10,940 --> 01:03:13,570
<font color="yellow">It's me, Gun Woo. Your father's acting weird.</font>

962
01:03:13,570 --> 01:03:15,070
<font color="yellow">Chairman Do Choong...</font>

963
01:03:15,070 --> 01:03:16,370
<font color="yellow">has dementia.</font>

964
01:03:16,740 --> 01:03:19,500
<font color="yellow">Cut your poor and useless son-in-law off.</font>

965
01:03:19,500 --> 01:03:20,970
<font color="yellow">Kang Gi Tan.</font>

966
01:03:20,970 --> 01:03:24,270
<font color="yellow">This is the last opportunity to avoid going against me.</font>

